{"tid":1382483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解俾物資唔得，但俾現金就得？有咩人會堅持要人俾現金呀？","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T19:36:46.000Z","uid":203889,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0e363cb9eee15c3c521d7b0889c88b7c4c9762","tid":1382483,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:16:05.000Z","msg":"點解俾物資唔得，但俾現金就得？有咩人會堅持要俾現金呀？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除左三毛我諗唔到仲有其他人</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好畀三毛帶風向<br />\n要幫，捐物資/捐裝/食物券一樣幫到<br />\n絕對唔好俾現金<br />\n同埋前線根本唔會收錢，佢地好多人連物資都唔敢收<br />\n<br />\n唯一重點：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好俾真金白銀，請直接買物資派</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d26b14e79fd3e006323031e8b0001efec58ceb6","tid":1382483,"uid":203889,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"轉發：呢個信息好重要！<br />\n<br />\n各位朋友麻煩下次出去主動問d 細路幫下佢地...依兩日好多group 已經見到佢地真係已經到左無飯食ge 階段...大家可以買定快餐店coupon 係身有需要就派...岩岩有位朋友講起...早兩日有幾個細路女真係主動問朋友有無野食，個時朋友買左餅比佢地...佢地講野好細聲無力個種黎...依家事後先諗返起佢地經濟應該真係出現左問題...肯主動搵人幫嘅唔多...麻煩咁多位大人主動d...無野食好易暈...有事想跑都跑唔郁...幫得一個得一個！！！！<br />\n<br />\n另外，我陳可樂親身經歷：雨傘97天我係靠朋友派百佳現金券維生，可以買牛奶同早餐。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家快去買現金券隨身攜帶！<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 唔好再問我成立基金，處理金錢好大責任，又要過audit, 又要俾公眾審核，好多道德問題。罷工基金都成日俾人屌，612人道基金都有人叫唔好捐。你話我發晦氣都係咁話，唔會處理現金既問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2560276963984560&amp;id=100000068448510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2560276963984560%26id%3D100000068448510&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=61236a11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2560276963984560&amp;id=100000068448510</a>"},{"pid":"2b5740eb7ca3c2d249ea21e523a218b8060ef774","tid":1382483,"uid":249040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"［飯券義助］推到人道基金、文宣入黎！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382261</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84b9cf35c804398aaefc293d02b02c4dec7544ee","tid":1382483,"uid":98431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:19:47.000Z","msg":"現金的確會落人口實<br />\n<br />\n請朋友食飯就唔會 送禮物又係另一回事"},{"pid":"5b7019f6a25f64405dd5c2a6243ad701285f9306","tid":1382483,"uid":187972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:20:12.000Z","msg":"建議三毛想要錢可以去遊行遊行完去鐵路站自助買飛機頂拎錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4911d5b59d1971124c1b0c1717ed1d13c915bf","tid":1382483,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84b9cf35c804398aaefc293d02b02c4dec7544ee","tid":1382483,"uid":98431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:19:47.000Z","msg":"現金的確會落人口實<br />\n<br />\n請朋友食飯就唔會 送禮物又係另一回事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:20:32.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n太多三毛，決定開po一次過貼"},{"pid":"9905fe8eac36058e76fa105e5518f1cf69f86b6d","tid":1382483,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9c527d4b9ca802d136da300111c1cf922b99ae4a","tid":1382483,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:28:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"831242495727eb6e7b4ee2c7c27a3bcc1fb66a44","tid":1382483,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:31:24.000Z","msg":"岩 咪撚ON9比錢<br />\n招人現眼"},{"pid":"b93d3db2c6b4150e8bbc062cab0fcbd43a186fd9","tid":1382483,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:35:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4265f5acfd90a836f53e69c66ead975d5253f39","tid":1382483,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:37:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff861278f313c4d6ed7b31b878d26df50696d439","tid":1382483,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T1